</span>
<br>
[[File:reader2.png|350px|frameless|center|link=]]

> Version: 0.3.35<br>
> Loading...<br>
> Initializing atmospheric sensors...

> SUCCESS!

> [10:23:52] AIR QUALITY INDEX: 128<br>
> [10:23:54] CH-335 LEVELS: 0.028%<br>
> [10:23:55] PM READINGS: 2.3<br>
> [10:23:57] OZONE (03) LEVELS: 68 ppb<br>
